    public interface EdgecutFragment<OID_T,VID_T,VDATA_T,EDATA_T>
extends FragmentBase<OID_T,VID_T,VDATA_T,EDATA_T>
    EdgecutFragment defines the interfaces of fragments with edgecut. To learn more about edge-cut and vertex-cut, please refers to https://spark.apache.org/docs/1.6.2/graphx-programming-guide.html#optimized-representation

    If we have an edge a-<b cutted by the partitioner, and a is in frag_0, and b in frag_1. Then:a-<b is a crossing edge, a is an inner_vertex in frag_0, b is an outer_vertex in frag_0.
